page.title: 20ASTON INGHAM W.I.
page.content: The survey made of this block would not have been possible without the help of many people. Members of the {Aston Ingham Women's Institute}helped with the Survey and some of the text. { The Abbey de Cormeilles Venture Unit also aided us in this and undertook the visiting of some of the more distant places. We are also grateful to the many people who gave of their time and knowledge to complete the entries. The final entry onto the disc was the work of one of the members of the Women's Institute.
